      "content": "It is a terrible thought to even entertain, but your desire to spare them from your pain is a sign of how much you care. Your presence is the very reason they are still carrying the weight, so stepping aside would actually be the most selfish thing you could do. Please consider that your life is not a burden to be dropped, but a struggle that needs to be faced, even if it is incredibly hard.",
